item.title: About me
item.description: Adaptable, hyperactive and tireless, I like challenges and adventures. I always wonder why things happen. I love to play team sports and climb, as well as improve my technical skills with CTFs. Work experience Angular developer [Apr 2018 - Aug 2018] Loccioni Group for Daimler - Stuttgart, Germany Three months of work in Daimler laboratories. I worked as a front-end developer of the framework used to control and manage the injectors test bench.
